OL,3,CMan who threatened to cut Jewish men's
OL,4,Cthroats pleads guilty
OL,6,FA man who threatened to cut Jewish
OL,7,Fmen's throats has pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fhate crime offences.
OL,10,FWayne Kelly admitted to verbally
OL,11,Fabusing the group while walking his
OL,12,Fdog on Northumberland Street in
OL,13,FSalford on May 6.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
