OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778274665
OL,3,CMan who threatened to cut Jewish men's
OL,4,Cthroats pleads guilty
OL,6,FThe Jewish men were on their way to a
OL,7,Fsynagogue when the 65 year old began
OL,8,Fhurling antisemitic abuse at them,
OL,9,Fincluding referring to historic
OL,10,Fatrocities against Jewish people. At
OL,11,Fone stage during the attack, he
OL,12,Fthreatened to go home to retrieve
OL,13,Fknives and cut their throats.
OL,15,FThe men contacted a helpline run by
OL,16,FJewish volunteers, and a local
OL,17,Fresident attended to help before Kelly
OL,18,Fremoved his coat and moved toward one
OL,19,Fof the men with clenched fists.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
