PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778274665
OL,3,CMan who threatened to cut Jewish men's
OL,4,Cthroats pleads guilty
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police arrested him
OL,7,Fat the scene, as he was led to the
OL,8,Fpolice vehicle, he shouted antisemitic
OL,9,Fabuse towards a Jewish child who was
OL,10,Fin the area. Kelly was charged within
OL,11,F24 hours of the offence.
OL,13,FHe appeared at Manchester Magistrates
OL,14,FCourt on Friday 8 May and will be
OL,15,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,17,FSarah Hammond, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,18,Ffor the Crown Prosecution Service,
OL,19,Fsaid, "The strength of the evidence
OL,20,Fleft Kelly with little option but to
OL,21,Fadmit the offences.
OL,26,@{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
