CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778274665
OL,3,CMan who threatened to cut Jewish men's
OL,4,Cthroats pleads guilty
OL,6,F"I would like to thank the victims who
OL,7,Fsupported this prosecution and hope
OL,8,Fthe speed of this prosecution
OL,9,Freassures them that we are determined
OL,10,Fto respond swiftly and decisively to
OL,11,Fhate in our communities.
OL,13,FOne of the victims later told police
OL,14,Fthat he recognised Kelly from a
OL,15,Fprevious incident on 12 March 2026,
OL,16,Fwhen Kelly had banged on his car while
OL,17,Fshouting antisemitic abuse.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
