OL,3,CMan who threatened to cut Jewish men's
OL,4,Cthroats pleads guilty
OL,6,FThe incident comes amid a reported
OL,7,Frise of antisemitism in the UK and
OL,8,Fjust weeks after two men were stabbed
OL,9,Fin London.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
